if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('SearchHistory') and o.name = 'FK_SEARCHHI_REFERENCE_USERS')
alter table SearchHistory
drop constraint FK_SEARCHHI_REFERENCE_USERS
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('Users') and o.name = 'FK_USERS_REFERENCE_ROLES')
alter table Users
drop constraint FK_USERS_REFERENCE_ROLES
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('Users')
and type = 'U')
drop table Users
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: Users */
/*==============================================================*/
create table Users (
UserId int not null,
Name varchar(50) not null,
Store varchar(50 null,
Account varchar(50) not null,
Password varchar(200) not null,
Salt varchar(200) not null,
RoleId int not null,
CreationDate datetime not null,
Enable bit not null,
constraint PK_USERS primary key (UserId)
)
go

alter table Users
add constraint FK_USERS_REFERENCE_ROLES foreign key (RoleId)
references Roles (RoleId)
go
